# <%= current_page.data.title %>


## Communication
Microsoft 365 is the Ministry of Justice's strategic productivity suite and includes Outlook, Teams, SharePoint, etc. We use Microsoft Teams for standups. 

## Slack

We use Slack for a lot of our communication, including updates outside of standup, quick questions, and general team discussions. 
We also use Slack huddles for pairing or direct calls.

